                    <textarea id="messageContent" rows="6" placeholder="‡∏û‡∏¥‡∏°‡∏û‡πå‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏ß‡πâ..." class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"></textarea>
                </div>
